for its clients the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the united states it invests in income and growth stocks trillium asset management llc is an employee owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to individuals and high net worth individuals it also caters to trusts corporate pension and profit sharing plans taft hartley plans charitable institutions for profit and non profit institutional clients foundations endowments municipalities registered mutual funds private investment funds and trust programs the firm manages separate clientfocused equity fixed income and balanced portfolios it also manages balanced mutual funds for its clients the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the united states it invests in income and growth stocks of companies across all capitalizations the firm employs garp and core investing style to make its equity investments it employs a topdown approach to select its sectors and a fundamental quantitative analysis and technical analysis to create its equity portfolio mix the firm benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against the sp  sp  and sp  indices for the fixed income portfolios it invests in investment grade intermediateterm corporate government agency and municipal bonds the firm makes socially and environmentally responsible communitybased investments it conducts inhouse research to make its investments trillium asset management was founded in  and is based in boston massachusetts with additional offices in san francisco california portland oregon and durham north carolina detailed description two financial center south streetsuite boston ma united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwtrilliuminvestcom key executives for trillium asset management llc mr matthew william patsky cfa chief executive officer managing partner and portfolio manager ms lesli o’connell cpa controller dr cheryl irene smith phd cfa managing partner chief compliance officer 